{"name":"Cause Mischief","type":"move","img":"icons/sundries/misc/teeth-dentures.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>craft a trap, cause a distraction, pull a prank, or otherwise introduce physical calamity to a situation</strong>, roll +Steam.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"basic","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>Your plan fails and you earn the ire of your target. Mark 1XP.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>Something goes awry. You manage to affect your target but an unintended side effect puts one or more of the Kids in peril. Describe what goes wrong and the Narrator will describe the new danger.</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>Things go according to your plan and you create an advantageous situation for yourself.</p>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"steam","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"VNTYUwRj6fNrFGgB"}
{"name":"Console","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-shadow-red.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>take a moment in a safe place to try to make another Kid feel better</strong>, describe what you do to comfort them and roll +Friendship with that character. Mend one relevant Harm on that character.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"basic","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>Describe how something or someone interferes with your attempt to heal.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>You both feel a little bit better, choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gain 1 Wish.</li>\n<li>Mark 1XP.</li>\n<li>The character you help gains +1 Friendship towards you.</li>\n</ul>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>Your help is exactly what they need, gain all three of these rewards.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gain 1 Wish.</li>\n<li>Mark 1XP.</li>\n<li>The character you help gains +1&nbsp;Friendship towards you.</li>\n</ul>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"prompt","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"h28zXSkIE0T2r4aR"}
{"name":"Face Your Fear","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-evil-horned-giant.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you would use another Move to act in direct defiance of your Fear, take a deep breath and roll with disadvantage.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"basic","rollFormula":"3d6kl2","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>Your Fear gets the best of you and your intended Move fails. Mark 1XP.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>Choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Succeed on your Move as if you rolled 10+.</li>\n<li>Reduce your Fear by 1 and fail your Move as if you rolled 6-.</li>\n</ul>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>Reduce your Fear by 1 and succeed on your Move as if you rolled a 10+.</p>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"formula","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"TMuoAKBncGQ4jiP4"}
{"name":"Make a Friend","type":"move","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-handshake.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>attempt to make friends with one of the Folk</strong>, describe how you make an appeal to them and roll +Mush.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"basic","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>They are wary of your intent and keep you at a distance. Mark 1XP.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>They are hesitant but can be convinced to be your friend.</p>\n<p>Choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>They ask you to make an unbreakable promise.</li>\n<li>They require a valuable gift in exchange for their friendship.</li>\n</ul>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>They respond well to your friendly advances. Choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>They give you a gift.</li>\n<li>They tell you important information.</li>\n<li>Gain 1 Wish.</li>\n</ul>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"mush","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"S07WwMgqgnc1LqSH"}
